headline: Humana Inc. to Release Fourth Quarter 2024 Results on February 11, 2025
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., January 09, 2025--Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM) will release its financial results for the fourth quarter 2024 (4Q24), as well as prepared management remarks (in PDF format), on Tuesday, February 11, 2025, at 6:30 a.m. Eastern time. The company will host a live question and answer session at 9:00 a.m. Eastern time that morning to discuss its financial results for the quarter and earnings guidance for 2025.
